Duration (weeks): 7
Online Course Fee: 4000.0
Platform: Infosys

--------OFFLINE COURSE DETAILS--------

Course: C++ Programming
Instructor: Kannimuthu
Duration (weeks): 10
Offline Course Fee: 9000.0
Location: Coimbatore

--------HYBRID COURSE DETAILS--------

Course: C Programming
Instructor: Praveen
Duration (weeks): 12
Hybrid Course Fee: 12000.0
Mode: Hybrid (Online: MongodB, Offline: College)
